abstract: Vivien Schweitzer reviews performance by Amphion String Quartet at Alice Tully Hall.
lead_paragraph: The Amphion ensemble performed Grieg’s one complete string quartet as part of its program on Sunday presented by the Chamber Music Society of Lincoln Center.
